<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚7点开始有烟花大会哦！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我从现在起<delay8 />就已经很期待了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />举办到半夜12点都没问题！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然能举行这么气派的活动，
<tag a="110" b="33" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可真厉害啊！。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
你已经做好心理准备了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么心理准备？<delay20 />当然是指今天的烟花大会啊！
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要看到烟花“啪”一声冲向高空，<delay8 />
什么烦恼都能忘掉！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />能不能快一点到夜里啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一看到你的脸就想起来了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天有烟花大会的哦，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有什么打算？
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和大家一起热热闹闹地欣赏也很好，<delay8 />
自己在家悠闲地欣赏也不错<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好令人烦恼呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">说起来，<tag a="110" b="3" />你
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />会感到紧张吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想呀，马上就是烟花大会了嘛。
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可不会为了这样的事情感到紧张哦！<delay frames="40" />
不过，毕竟庆典就快开始了，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也有好好打起精神来。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<delay20 />再过一会儿<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是烟花大会了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天会燃放怎样的烟花呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我好期待啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说回来，幸好今天是晴天啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟是难得的烟花大会，<delay8 />
当然想要烟花盛放得美丽一些。
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />精心制作它，<delay8 />让它声势浩大地绽放，<delay8 />
这和培育花朵的道理是一样的。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经迫不及待了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay20 />虽然烟花大会已经结束，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过在我的心里，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花还在接二连三地盛放呢！
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />今天玩得太欢腾了，<delay8 />
都不舍得去睡觉呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />庆典结束后的氛围，<delay8 />
我还挺喜欢的。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过我现在还不想一个人待着，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能和<tag a="110" b="3" />你说说话，
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太好了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花放完后，<delay8 />
突然就变得好寂静啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我比较喜欢热闹的气氛，<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以每天都举办烟花大会
也没问题哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花大会真是太让人开心了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的烟花也就此结束了啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />内心觉得寂寥也是没有办法的事。
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过一想到明年也能<delay8 />
和这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上的伙伴一起观看烟花，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就一点都不觉得落寞了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说回来，<delay8 />今年的烟花
是我见过最美的啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这1个月来，<delay8 />每逢星期天都有烟花大会，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都让我有点不知道接下来的星期天<delay8 />
要怎么度过了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年最后的烟花<delay8 />
也气派地升空了呀！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花的声响还在胸口回荡，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚有可能直到早晨
都兴奋得睡不着呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />　</message>
</msbt>